      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a great fit for someone looking for a reliable driver that needs a little cosmetic and mechanical attention. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear in the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that just needs some TLC to bring it back to its best.",
