    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one and it honestly still feels brand new. Whether you're cruising around town or headed on a road trip, you're going to love how smooth and perfect this ride is. It's been kept sparkling clean and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
