    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a meticulously maintained double-VANOS variable valve timing system. This specimen utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a torque-sensing M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring surgical power delivery to the rear wheels. The chassis remains structurally flawless, benefiting from comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a suspension setup that retains its factory-spec damping and rebound characteristics. Every mechanical interface, from the rod bearings to the throttle actuators, has been preserved to exacting standards, delivering an uncompromised, high-performance analog driving experience.",
      "price": 46500.0,
