    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Finished in a stunning, deep metallic paint that remains entirely free of swirls, chips, or imperfections, this car has been meticulously garage-kept and climate-controlled throughout its life. The interior is equally pristine; the leather seats still retain their factory-fresh scent and firm bolstering, with no signs of wear on the bolsters or steering wheel. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the adaptive cruise control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach\u2014serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a full, documented history. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or oxidation. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection and a 'no-stories' history, this is the ultimate example.",
      "price": 48500.0,
